c: 24
v: 54
t: "Ithi, “hloniphani uMvelinqangi futhi nihloniphe isithunywa kepha uma nifulathela kuphela okwaso ngumthwalo obekwe kusona futhi okwenu ngumthwalo obekwe phezu kwenu futhi uma nisihlonipha (isithunywa) niyobe niholeke ngendlela eqondile futhi awukho umsebenzi ophezu kwesithunywa ngaphandle kokudlulisela umyalezo ngendlela ecacile"